<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Desi Sip - Authentic Indian Buttermilk</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#fffdf6;
color:#333;
line-height:1.6;
}

/* Header */

header{
background:#2e7d32;
color:white;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
}

header h1{
font-size:40px;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

header p{
font-size:18px;
opacity:0.9;
}

/* Hero */

.hero{
padding:60px 20px;
text-align:center;
background:#fff3cd;
}

.hero h2{
font-size:36px;
margin-bottom:15px;
color:#2e7d32;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
}

/* Products */

.products{
padding:60px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.products h2{
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:40px;
color:#2e7d32;
}

.product-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
gap:30px;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

.product{
background:white;
padding:25px;
border-radius:12px;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
transition:0.3s;
}

.product:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px);
}

.product h3{
color:#2e7d32;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.price{
font-weight:bold;
color:#ff9800;
font-size:18px;
}

/* About */

.about{
padding:60px 20px;
background:#f4f7f4;
text-align:center;
}

.about h2{
font-size:30px;
margin-bottom:20px;
color:#2e7d32;
}

.about p{
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
font-size:17px;
}

/* Footer */

footer{
background:#2e7d32;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
margin-top:40px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Desi Sip</h1>
<p>Authentic Indian Buttermilk</p>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Refreshment Straight From Indian Tradition</h2>
<p>Desi Sip brings the authentic taste of traditional Indian buttermilk with modern quality and hygiene. Healthy, refreshing, and perfect for every day.</p>
</section>

<section class="products">

<h2>Our Flavours</h2>

<div class="product-grid">

<div class="product">
<h3>Classic Masala Chaas</h3>
<p>Traditional spiced buttermilk with roasted cumin.</p>
<p class="price">₹30</p>
</div>

<div class="product">
<h3>Mint Jeera Chaas</h3>
<p>Refreshing mint flavor with jeera twist.</p>
<p class="price">₹35</p>
</div>

<div class="product">
<h3>Spicy Punjabi Chaas</h3>
<p>Bold and spicy buttermilk for real desi taste.</p>
<p class="price">₹35</p>
</div>

<div class="product">
<h3>Himalayan Salt Chaas</h3>
<p>Light and healthy with pink Himalayan salt.</p>
<p class="price">₹40</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="about">

<h2>About Desi Sip</h2>

<p>
Desi Sip is an Indian beverage brand focused on bringing traditional buttermilk (chaas) to modern consumers. Our drinks are made using authentic recipes, fresh ingredients, and a commitment to healthy refreshment.
</p>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Desi Sip | Indian Buttermilk Brand</p>

</footer>

</body>
  </html>
